(25, 3, 'It contained significant inaccuracies regarding the witnesses'' behavior and their number.'),
(25, 4, 'It was based on police reports that were later confirmed by independent investigators.'),

(26, 1, 'helping behavior is actually the norm rather than the exception in real-world emergencies'),
